Interface Transformation


  • public interface Transformation
    Image transformation.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      java.lang.String key()
      Returns a unique key for the transformation, used for caching purposes.
      RequestHandler.Result transform(RequestHandler.Result source)
      Transform the source result into a new result.

    • Method Detail

      • transform

        RequestHandler.Result transform(RequestHandler.Result source)
        Transform the source result into a new result. If you create a new bitmap instance, you must call Bitmap.recycle() on source. You may return the original if no transformation is required.

      • key

        java.lang.String key()
        Returns a unique key for the transformation, used for caching purposes. If the transformation has parameters (e.g. size, scale factor, etc) then these should be part of the key.
